      "id": "note-1770846551473-1",
      "title": "START (FEATURE)",
      "content": "This workflow guides the implementation of a new feature from design proposal through testing.\n\nResponsibility:\n- #claude: Design, implementation, technical decisions\n- #grigri: Requirements, approval, testing, feedback\n\nFlow: Design → Review → Implement → Test → Complete\n\n#claude #grigri",
      "hashtags": [
        "#claude",
        "#grigri"
      ],
      "fields": {},
      "position": {
        "x": 42.2107567523916,
        "y": -651.3244771752895
