    },
    {
      "id": "note-1770848470111-9",
      "title": "Implement the approved plan",
      "content": "Claude implements the feature, issues, or fixes.\n\nOnce complete, move to USER TESTING.\n\n#claude",
      "hashtags": [
        "#claude"
      ],
      "fields": {
