    {
      "id": "note-1770848473986-10",
      "title": "commit & push",
      "content": "grigri is using the app via github-pages so you'll need to commit changes and push before he can test changes.\n\nBe sure to update the version number in the JS and CSS, as well as the landing page. Display the current version in the CLI.\n#claude",
