    {
      "id": "note-1770848485487-12",
      "title": "Test",
      "content": "#grigri\n\nGrigri tests the feature and provides feedback.\n2. Grigri will either:\n     a) request further edits\n     b) approve/affirm the feature is completed\n\n\n\nIf issues found: Claude fixes and returns to this step.\nIf approved: Proceed to COMPLETE.\n\n#grigri",
      "hashtags": [
        "#grigri"
      ],
