      "title": "Update documentation",
      "content": "1. Update all relevant documentation.\n2. Show which documentation files were updated.\n3. If anything worked well about this workflow, notify grigri\n4. Similarly, if anything could be improved in this workflow, notify grigri.\n\n#claude ",
