    },
    {
      "id": "note-1771054422094-9",
      "title": "DESIGN PROPOSAL",
      "content": "Claude proposes the design.\n\nInclude:\n1. Technical approach - How will this be implemented?\n2. Files affected - Which files need changes?\n3. Open questions - What needs clarification?\n4. Estimated scope - How much work?\n\n#claude",
      "hashtags": [
        "#claude"
      ],
      "fields": {},
      "position": {
        "x": -259.5818365409425,
        "y": -306.19755454934204
      },
      "zIndex": 0,
      "children": [],
      "childEdges": [],
      "created": "2026-02-14T07:33:42.094Z",
      "modified": "2026-02-15T06:00:15.231Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "note-1771054422094-10",
      "title": "USER REVIEW & APPROVAL",
      "content": "Grigri reviews the proposal and provides feedback.\n\nRespond with:\n1. Approval or requested changes\n2. Clarifications on requirements\n3. Priority or scope adjustments\n4. Any constraints or concerns\n\nOnce approved, Claude proceeds to IMPLEMENTATION.\n\n#grigri",
      "hashtags": [
        "#grigri"
      ],
      "fields": {},
      "position": {
        "x": -256.24189001059233,
        "y": -181.7017175041238
      },
      "zIndex": 0,
      "children": [],
      "childEdges": [],
      "created": "2026-02-14T07:33:42.094Z",
      "modified": "2026-02-15T05:54:55.211Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "note-1771054422095-13",
      "title": "COMPLETE",
      "content": "Feature is approved and deployed.\n\nNext steps:\n1. Document design decision in decision-history.md (if major)\n2. Update ROADMAP.txt\n3. Close any related issues\n\n#claude #grigri",
